content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.75 - Parcel check and/or excess value check to be issued for each parcel checked

State Regulations
A parcel check shall be issued for each parcel checked. If excess value is declared, an excess value check shall be issued. Parcels
will be delivered upon presentation of the parcel check and excess value check, if any, issued by the Port Authority. Notes
